    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained, making it a reliable choice for any driver. The engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts exactly as it should, providing a comfortable and dependable driving experience. While there are a few minor cosmetic blemishes consistent with its age, such as small stone chips on the front bumper, the interior is clean and all electronics are fully functional. This car is ready for the road and would make an excellent daily driver for someone seeking quality without the new-car price tag.",
