    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have to see this absolute gem! It\u2019s in incredible condition and honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, so it\u2019s spotless inside and out and drives like a dream. If you\u2019re looking for something that feels brand new without the sticker shock, this is the one for you. Come say hi and take it for a spin!",
