    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This vehicle is an absolute time capsule, meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment and maintained to the highest possible standards. The exterior finish is flawless, retaining its deep factory luster with no evidence of rock chips, swirl marks, or door dings. Every panel gap is laser-straight, and the undercarriage is as clean as the bodywork. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom state; the premium leather seats show no signs of bolster wear, the dashboard is crack-free, and that distinct 'new car' scent still lingers. All electronic systems, from the infotainment to the dual-zone climate control, function perfectly with crisp tactile feedback on every button. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, featuring a comprehensive service history with every fluid flush and inspection performed ahead of schedule. It sits on pristine alloy wheels with brand-new performance tires, offering a driving experience that is tight, quiet, and indistinguishable from its original delivery day. For the collector or enthusiast who demands perfection without compromise, this is the definitive example.",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
